{"tid":1905383,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"市民郊遊避疫　鶴咀人頭湧湧大部分人士不戴口罩","createTime":"2020-03-01T08:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T09:52:11.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d76889124883d88ded37e62e2a5a1b1dc1cd4f","tid":1905383,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T08:25:00.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒疫情肆虐，有人為了避開人煙稠密的市區，紛紛選擇到郊遊，令到多個山頭人來人往。周末一朝早，筲箕灣往石澳的巴士總站已經大排長龍，有經常行山市民表示，人流比以往多出一半，但認為郊外較空曠，空氣較流通，故不太擔心。<br />\n<br />\n疫情嚴重，但在鶴咀大部分行山人士也沒有戴上口罩，在「打卡位」蟹洞更是擠滿拍照的行山人士。<br />\n<br />\n俗稱武漢肺炎的新型冠狀病毒疫情肆虐，有人為了避開人煙稠密的市區，紛紛選擇郊遊，令多個山頭人來人往。周末一朝早，筲箕灣往石澳的巴士總站已經大排長龍，有經常行山市民表示，人流比以往多出一半，但認為郊外較空曠，空氣較流通，故不太擔心。<br />\n<br />\n疫情嚴重，但在鶴咀大部分行山人士也沒有戴上口罩，在「打卡位」蟹洞更是擠滿拍照的行山人士。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082298/org/2204e529a62ba974f264e4fa4eb363cb.jpg/MXoT9VHIaVSLOemXA5stnfCkXvlKdHaRMj91NBg_dTQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082298%2Forg%2F2204e529a62ba974f264e4fa4eb363cb.jpg%2FMXoT9VHIaVSLOemXA5stnfCkXvlKdHaRMj91NBg_dTQ&h=e9a82d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082296/org/4eeef8e8e363eeaf9698828215f843d4.jpg/JMaKWTZa89UzYP0j5yOlwfhwSud6BzDnF3rw4j168OI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082296%2Forg%2F4eeef8e8e363eeaf9698828215f843d4.jpg%2FJMaKWTZa89UzYP0j5yOlwfhwSud6BzDnF3rw4j168OI&h=7125b83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082294/org/95ba82a7a748e1a4efa408c8c40614cd.jpg/0OO0ZEgy0NzoMqGRk3IZ6IjLofJWlEGqG7UpPDG1KTw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082294%2Forg%2F95ba82a7a748e1a4efa408c8c40614cd.jpg%2F0OO0ZEgy0NzoMqGRk3IZ6IjLofJWlEGqG7UpPDG1KTw&h=d4e4f8ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082297/org/c7757e5bbdbb447ba8492065cacfbaec.jpg/pDOcg_UYL1-thvcRiMdpWoZ6yiAI9kprtVZuy