Fe6047c0142f1b60d62a242d52c24eb2f.jpg%2F9KuNsY1hPlnxdUqF9CC8S74ZycTOKYzmW9UEQ3HVBEM&h=c83001d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082318/org/15baab6f2e84831277fab10799eee867.jpg/kDk6CxflYeiM1iXVOPsVTpp_G9N_dhJVGEAQIzJAECM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082318%2Forg%2F15baab6f2e84831277fab10799eee867.jpg%2FkDk6CxflYeiM1iXVOPsVTpp_G9N_dhJVGEAQIzJAECM&h=cf3b8334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082314/org/cb09d74cb143c64835f750c18370a83d.jpg/hv8IeZOHixLBIxe615yVix25COLEczWYr-fZqIXn2ag\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082314%2Forg%2Fcb09d74cb143c64835f750c18370a83d.jpg%2Fhv8IeZOHixLBIxe615yVix25COLEczWYr-fZqIXn2ag&h=97a0f08e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082315/org/ecd2ac321e5afbb591bb34749b2fcd32.jpg/VatCJcSXIj30OOcLrzvOSDx6wGK3yb3j3OXbs_bl27M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082315%2Forg%2Fecd2ac321e5afbb591bb34749b2fcd32.jpg%2FVatCJcSXIj30OOcLrzvOSDx6wGK3yb3j3OXbs_bl27M&h=2cdb8900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082313/org/298bced5f00cb55f325f025a167bcba8.jpg/6TrOJF7U1cJTebKghkUA3xB82t2147gG5S4tZs8uLWY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082313%2Forg%2F298bced5f00cb55f325f025a167bcba8.jpg%2F6TrOJF7U1cJTebKghkUA3xB82t2147gG5S4tZs8uLWY&h=4dd3abfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082317/org/dab325d4845f36718f9754dab24c91a0.jpg/wsB_7jbuC8DA2PChR06I9-kG8cr-76AMgOiXw6rol8M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082317%2Forg%2Fdab325d4845f36718f9754dab24c91a0.jpg%2FwsB_7jbuC8DA2PChR06I9-kG8cr-76AMgOiXw6rol8M&h=31189559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082319/org/694b6e8982ec16d0f28cad8e82e64c33.jpg/WENyVQOMn6J9OLMJrDmAsLydu-y8zw0HgIDOQ6qAzkM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082319%2Forg%2F694b6e8982ec16d0f28cad8e82e64c33.jpg%2FWENyVQOMn6J9OLMJrDmAsLydu-y8zw0HgIDOQ6qAzkM&h=be7ee81b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4082321/org/c8a790c1dfe9e5e2d1ff67acb13a4c4d.jpg/zOIuqejWvmZ7om6yN_xhuZpCzUkyTJFwAzAZdykwGXc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4082321%2Forg%2Fc8a790c1dfe9e5e2d1ff67acb13a4c4d.jpg%2FzOIuqejWvmZ7om6yN_xhuZpCzUkyTJFwAzAZdykwGXc&h=215599e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一向有行山習慣的楊氏夫婦，早幾年亦曾到鶴咀，認為今日人流多出一半。（曾凱欣攝）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>往石澳巴士爆滿　有行山人士不打算戴口罩</strong><br />\n<br />\n早上十時多，在筲箕灣巴士總站已經人頭湧湧，多架往石澳，路線途經龍脊及鶴咀等熱門行山路線的巴士亦爆滿。<br />\n<br />\n雖然疫情嚴重，但行山人士陳先生認為行山期間若戴上口罩太過侷促，故沒有打算配戴口罩。他直言「唔擔心得咁多」，又指到空曠的地方，即使人多「都無咁驚」；同行的女友亦相信，只要多做運動，增強自身的體抗力，自然更有效對抗疫情。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日有不少行山人士，隨意在山頭亂拋垃圾，陳先生認為行為「不知所謂」，指行山人士應該儘量避免製造垃圾，以及自己垃圾應自己帶走。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>周小姐不介意人流增加：座山又唔係你嘅</strong><br />\n<br />\n與友人一行三人的周小姐表示，平日都有行山的習慣，她的丈夫指自己經常行山，覺得今日人流有所增加，相信與疫情下較多人選擇行山有關。周小姐又指，到人多的地方為了保護自己亦會戴上口罩，「有山風應該舒服啲」。對於人流增加，周小姐表示不介意，直言山頭是公眾地方「座山又唔係你嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>鶴咀道泊滿私家車「打卡位」更見人頭湧湧</strong><br />\n<br />\n在鶴咀道，路邊停泊了不少私家車，但暫未見有阻塞行車路的情況。大批行山人士沿鶴咀道步行至鶴咀海岸保護區，入口豎起「無線電台範圍 非因工事請勿進入」的告示牌，惟不少人跨過欄杆入內，保護區內的「打卡位」蟹洞更見人頭湧湧。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有行山人士形容今日人流比以往多出一半</strong><br />\n<br />\n一向有行山習慣的楊氏夫婦，早幾年亦曾到鶴咀，認為今日人流多出一半，雖然人多，但夫婦並沒有戴上口罩，認為郊外較空曠，空氣較流通，故不太擔心，但若遇到多人的情況都會盡量避開，先退其他人通過。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：曾凱欣"},{"pid":"0fa0a8286f9b5f4bb2453f0e68ad0a13cf467bd4","tid":1905383,"uid":47311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T08:32:19.000Z","msg":"幾時開始戶外係冇事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eabc306c65c1b04eee256d467a1ad85ad0a09b7","tid":1905383,"uid":280329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"多得呢d人先可以社區爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7aca51a0ea70ec529d990502348e2703748b384","tid":1905383,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"連登行山撚又出動"},{"pid":"93be27b41f6eb25b8a84b6a0c115b8b941238bc1","tid":1905383,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T08:56:39.000Z","msg":"攬炒"},{"pid":"69d97d15cf0fda5215ba2221372c03e76dc6ddc3","tid":1905383,"uid":81756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0eabc306c65c1b04eee256d467a1ad85ad0a09b7","tid":1905383,"uid":280329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"多得呢d人先可以社區爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"下次集會入去行山熱點 和你塞 等班賤種港豬食下椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}